    {
      "id": "df9521b8-0491-4188-af18-5d6acfc7605e",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "To address the issue, authors propose a new method FCIKT that attempts to make a more complete representation of these phenomena. The main idea is to use a fusion module to cross features and organize them with graph convolutional networks. The model also incorporates attention mechanisms and GRU to dinamically capture and update student knowledge state before the final prediction.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "df9521b8-0491-4188-af18-5d6acfc7605e",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
          "page_id": "d4dbe55d-5d93-4ed6-b8b4-1c318d6b003a"
        },
        "created_time": "2024-08-06T16:20:00.000Z",
        "last_edited_time": "2024-08-06T16:23:00.000Z",
